title: Jewelpet Movie: Sweets Dance Princess
synopsis: The story of the new film is set in Sweetsland, a country next to Jewelland. Ruby and the other Jewelpets are celebrating the birthday of the princess with dancing. However, during the preparations for the birthday party, a mysterious object appears from the skies. In the object is a Sweetspet boy, whose identity is unknown.
voices: ['Saitou, Ayaka', 'Sasaki, Nozomi', 'Hirano, Aya', 'Ashida, Mana', 'Shimizu, Ai', 'Kobayashi, Yumiko', 'Sawashiro, Miyuki', 'Toyosaki, Aki', 'Fukuyama, Jun', 'Kaida, Yuki']
